Class House.Cuboid

  • java.lang.Object
    • House.Cuboid
  • Enclosing class:
    House
    public class House.Cuboid
extends java.lang.Object
    This class represents a room which is Cuboidal in shape. The room is made up of 6 rectangular walls.
